   1 &amp; \gamma  &amp; {{\gamma ^2}}  \cr 

 } } \right|$$<br><br>On expanding along C<sub>1</sub>, we get<br><br>$$ = (\alpha  - \beta )(\beta  - \gamma ).1[\beta  + \gamma  - \alpha  - \beta ]$$<br><br>$$ = (\alpha  - \beta )(\beta  - \gamma )(\gamma  - \alpha )$$

