 } } \right]$$<br><br>$$\therefore$$ $${C_{11}} = 1 - 3 \times 0 = 1$$<br><br>$${C_{12}} =  - (2 - 0) =  - 2$$<br><br>$${C_{13}} = 2 \times 3 - 0 \times 1 = 6$$<br><br>$${C_{21}} =  - (0 \times 1 - 3 \times 2) = 6$$<br><br>$${C_{22}} = 1 \times 1 - 0 \times 2 = 1$$<br><br>$${C_{23}} =  - (1 \times 3 - 0 \times 1) =  - 3$$<br><br>$${C_{31}} = 0 - 1 \times 2 =  - 2$$<br><br>$${C_{32}} =  - (1 \times 0 - 2 \times 2) = 4$$<br><br>$${C_{33}} = 1 \times 1 - 2 \times 0 = 1$$<br><br>$$\therefore$$ adj $$A = {\left[ {\matrix{
