 } } \right|$$<br><br>Area of $$\Delta$$ABC<br><br>$$A\left( {{x_1},{1 \over {{x_1}}}} \right),B\left( {{x_2},{1 \over {{x_2}}}} \right),C\left( {{x_3},{1 \over {{x_3}}}} \right)$$<br><br>$$ = {1 \over 2}\left| {\matrix{
