 } } \right|$$<br><br>$$ = \left| {{{({x_1} - {x_2})({x_2} - {x_3})({x_3} - {x_1})} \over {2{x_1}{x_2}{x_3}}}} \right|$$

We have,<br><br>p + q + r = 0 and a + b + c = 0<br><br>Now, $$\left| {\matrix{
